  "reference_number": "RUS2624",
  "remarks": "\nELECTRONIC SCIENTIFIC ENGINEERING LTD is an “ involved person\" under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the following grounds: ELECTRONIC SCIENTIFIC ENGINEERING LTD is or has been involved in destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine by providing goods or technology that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine.\n",
